data.description: Nestled on a charming corner lot, this property exudes curb appeal with its well-maintained landscaping and the shade of mature trees that provide both beauty and a touch of tranquility.  This comfortable and stylish home, boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a spacious 3-car garage.  Step through the front door and discover a flowing floor plan that effortlessly connects the living spaces. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen featuring modern appliances, a large pantry, and a large breakfast nook. The living room is bathed in natural light and has a gorgeous fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. With four bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or even a home office.  Broken Arrow School District.
